  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    £260 million announced for the Borderlands growth deal
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  
  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Scotland is set to benefit from new funding for a Borderlands growth deal the Chancellor announced in the Spring Statement
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="column-two-thirds metadata-column">
